 native diversity, nature tourism, and opportunities for recreational hunting. We thus use some of the emergent issues related to wind farm development in the LGC\u2014such as siting turbines on cropland sites as opposed to on native rangelands\u2014to illustrate the kinds of challenges and opportunities that wildlife managers must face as we balance our demand for sustainable energy with the need to conserve and sustain bird migration routes and corridors, native vertebrates, and the habitats that support them.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Kuvlesky, William P.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Brennan, Leonard A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Morrison, Michael L.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Boydston, Kathy K.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ballard, Bart M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Bryant, Fred C.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/497829c7b2a29e0e1644c4d66b428a74", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/186aafd82f0c01d4b26b35f5549d5962c761b789a78f96ce62aa2be91ab6a370", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/CXVP2GVZ", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/CXVP2GVZ", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/36ed63d0a83d1eeeab5a2afdce70fc3d!/b101126-103686", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journ